    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037348_7_14437-14535",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14437-14535",
      "markText": "这倒并非因为想驳斥“原始民族主义”或“反帝国主义”的老调，而是因为三元里事件在后来的20年里，是中国南方发生如此众多问题的一个关键的前奏，如团练运动、太平天国运动、秘密社会、宗族斗争、排外运动等。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037348&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14437&rangeEnd=14535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23032c90813ab7516g018b6c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14437&rangeEnd=14535"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037348_8_6932-7016",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6932-7016",
      "markText": "对于林则徐和晚清时期的一些官员来说，儒家史学中的民是无法估量的，民众可以拯救一切或摧毁一切，也可以重建或推翻一切。即使经历了一而再、再而三的失败，这个信念却丝毫未动摇。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037348&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6932&rangeEnd=7016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23032c90813ab7516g018b6c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6932&rangeEnd=7016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037348_6_510-537",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "510-537",
      "markText": "连续15年的屠杀和饥荒，让中国丧失了约一两千万条人命。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037348&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=510&rangeEnd=537",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23032c90813ab7516g018b6c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=510&rangeEnd=537"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300037348_10_15867-15937",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "15867-15937",
      "markText": "可以理解人们需要替罪羊。政敌必须被贬到无处不在的“汉奸”行列里。英国人又够不着，而那些日积月累的挫折感、无望、恐惧只能对身边近处的目标发泄。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300037348&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=15867&rangeEnd=15937",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/23032c90813ab7516g018b6c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=15867&rangeEnd=15937"
